    <lb n="1"/>Πα<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν</supplied>εχώτης ὁ καὶ Πανάρης τῶν κεκοσμητευκότων τῆς Ὀξυρυγχειτῶν 

    <lb n="2"/>πόλεως διὰ Γεμέλλου φίλου Ἀπολλωνίῳ <choice><corr>σημειογράφῳ</corr><sic>σημιογραφω</sic></choice> χαίρειν. συνέστησά σοι 

    <lb n="3"/>Χαιράμμωνα δοῦλον πρὸς μάθησιν σημείων ὧν ἐπίσταται ὁ υἱός <subst><add place="inline">σου</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">μου</del></subst> 

    <lb n="4"/>Δι<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ο</supplied>νύσιος ἐπὶ χρόνον ἔτη δύο <num value="2"/> ἀπὸ τοῦ ἐνεστῶτος μηνὸς Φαμενὼθ τοῦ 

    <lb n="5"/>ὀκτωκαιδεκάτου ἔτους Ἀντωνίνου Καίσαρος τοῦ κυρίου μισθοῦ τοῦ συμπεφω-

    <lb n="6"/>νημένου πρὸς ἀλλήλους ἀργυρίου δραχμῶν ἑκατὸν εἴκοσι <num value="120"/> χωρὶς ἑορτι-

    <lb n="7"/>κῶν, ἐξ ὧν ἔσχες τὴν πρώτην δόσιν ἐν <subst><add place="inline">δραχμαῖς</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">δραγμαις</del></subst> τεσσαράκοντα <num value="40"/>, τὴν δὲ 

    <lb n="8"/>δευτέραν <choice><corr>λήψει</corr><sic>ληψη</sic></choice> τοῦ παιδὸς ἀνειληφότος τὸ κο<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">μ</unclear>εντάρ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ι</supplied>ον ὅλον ἐν δρα-

    <lb n="9"/>χ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">μ</supplied>αῖς τ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">εσσ</supplied>αράκοντα <num value="40"/>, τὴν δὲ τρίτην λήψομαι ἐπὶ τέλει τοῦ χρόνου τοῦ 

    <lb n="10"/>παιδὸς ἐκ παντὸς λόγου πεζοῦ γράφοντος καὶ <choice><corr>ἀναγιγνώσκοντος</corr><sic>αναγεινωσ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">κον</supplied>τος</sic></choice> ἀμέμπτως 

    <lb n="11"/>τὰς <sic>δὲ</sic> λοιπὰς δραχμὰς τεσσαράκοντα <num value="40"/>. ἐὰν δὲ ἐντὸς τοῦ χ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ρ</supplied>όνου αὐτὸν 

    <lb n="12"/>ἀπαρτίσῃς οὐκ <subst><add place="inline">ἐκδέξομαι</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">εκδεχομαι</del></subst> τὴν προκειμένην προθεσμ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ί</supplied>αν, οὐκ ἐξόντος 

    <lb n="13"/>μοι ἐντὸς τοῦ χρόνου τὸν παῖδα ἀποσπᾶν, παραμενεῖ δέ σ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ο</supplied>ι μετὰ <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τὸ</supplied>ν χρό<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">νον ὅσας</supplied> 

    <lb n="14"/>ἐὰν ἀργήσῃ ἡμέρας ἢ μῆνας. <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="18">ιη</num> Αὐτοκράτορος Καίσαρος Τίτου Αἰλίου Ἁδριανοῦ 

    <lb n="15"/><choice><corr>Ἀντωνίνου</corr><sic>αντωνεινου</sic></choice> Σεβαστοῦ Εὐσεβοῦς Φαμενὼθ <num value="5">ε</num>. </ab></div><div n="meta.20424" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.20424" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" value="0155-03-01" notBefore="155" notAfter="155">1. März 155</date></p></div><div n="meta.20424" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Vgl. Comunicazioni 5, 2003, S. 20-23.</p></div><div n="meta.20424" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head></div><div n="meta.20424" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">4</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">724</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">20424</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">4</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">724</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0181;4;724" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.20424" type="bibliography" subtype="corrections" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">181</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">XI</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">145</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.20424" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p